Knocking triggers the passive buzzer which starts a melody that can be stopped by the press of a button.

Implementation with no delay() usage.
Components:
-1 x arduino board
-1 x usbToArduino cable
-11 x connection cables
-1 active buzzer
-1 pushbutton
-1 circular thing the teacher gave us as a substitute for the passive buzzer (the passive buzzer didnt work)
